text: WEO may refer to: * Warehouse Economy Outlet, a 1970s American discount supermarket chain operated by A&P; * World Economic Outlook, a half-yearly publication published by International Monetary Fund * World Energy Outlook, an annual publication * World Eskimo Indian Olympics, formerly known as the World Eskimo Olympics == See also == * WEOS, call letters for a radio station in Geneva, New York * Weo, a settlement in Nauru
title: WEO
